Custom Docs Site

Personal Documentation Template version 0.1

Get Started →

Simplicity First

Minimal setup with markdown-centered project structure helps you focus on writing.

Vue-Powered

Enjoy the dev experience of Vue + webpack, use Vue components in markdown, and develop custom themes with Vue.

Performance

VuePress generates pre-rendered static HTML for each page, and runs as an SPA once a page is loaded.

Other Features

Custom containers, Line highlighting, Line numbers, Import code snippets, Vue Templating, Vue Components, Responsive layout, Optional homepage, Simple out-of-the-box header-based search, algolia search, Customizable navbar and sidebar, Auto-generated github links and page edit links, PWA, last Updated, Multilingual support, Blog Theme and Plugins(Blog Plugin, Search , PWA, Google analytics)
